      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector's dream. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, with every feature and system functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment.",
