      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean, showing only minor surface scratches and small rock chips expected from regular driving. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as intended. It represents a solid, reliable choice for a buyer looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
